            "path": "src/components/SocialAccounts.js",
            "comments": [
                "First, bring in React, then whatever additional components you'll need (you probably want to grab [[sym-text:clsx(ff8eac86-dbd4-440a-8f16-b8041df2082b)]] unless you're not generating any markup at all). After that, import your component styles."
            ]
        },
        {
